public class FractalIO
extends Object

Fractal Input and Output Reads and writes .frc files. .frc files contain the values for fractal definition
FORMAT FOR FILE
====================
AXIOM(string)
FSTRING(string)
fSTRING(string)
XSTRING(string)
YSTRING(string)
ROTATION(double)
INITIAL_DIRECTION(double)
FLENGTH(double)
REDUCTION FACTOR(double)
LEVEL(double)
RANDOM FACTOR(double)
